<title>yào bǎ jiào huì jiàn zào zài zhè pán shí shàng 迦南907</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yào bǎ jiào huì jiàn zào zài zhè pán shí shàng, yīn jiān de quán bǐng bù néng shèng guò tā.
 yào bǎ jiào huì jiàn zào zài zhè pán shí shàng, yīn jiān de quán bǐng bù néng shèng guò tā.
 tā shì shén ér zi, tā shì shén gāo yáng, tā shì fù huó zhǔ, yáng de dà mù zhě.
 wàn gǔ de pán shí, yǒng yuǎn de jūn wáng. tā shì yé sū jī dū.</lyrics>
</song>